To build NVthreads library, type the following commands:
    cd $NVthreads/src
    make

Your NVthreads library named libnvthread.so will be compiled and ready to use at:
    $NVthreads/src/libnvthread.so

To link your application to NVthreads library
    gcc -o foo.o foo.c -ldl -rdynamic $NVthreads/src/libnvthread.so

Special compiler flags:
    ENABLE_PROFILING: collect metadata for statistics
    PAGE_DENSITY: collect the average percentage of touched bytes in each page

